{"tid":502924,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點開口問男友？","createTime":"2017-12-18T11:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T15:30:19.000Z","uid":163373,"like":7,"dislike":106,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"965d633da0cdf484b6fdbd8f7ff18c16d8838585","tid":502924,"uid":163373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:19:00.000Z","msg":"知道左佢有另一個，喺電話問過佢但佢冇出聲，之後wts再問又唔應機<br />\n呢幾日wts佢都唔多應我，今日終於約到佢星期五食飯，應該點開口<br />\n我怕一問佢又覺得我chur、嫌我煩，好似推緊個男友去第二個女人度<br />\n我當然想自己係唯一，就算唔得都拜托你揀定一個啦，成日幻想佢陪緊另一個，同我講好忙然後就陪女，好辛苦"},{"pid":"4c10035fe46099b14e62493bcab230493c56d4dc","tid":502924,"uid":13467,"like":149,"dislike":3,"score":146,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:20:25.000Z","msg":"知道仲唔分手?<br />\n留係到做免費雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"8909d77ec4d3ae55bd5efb94b6a65f40deadcdcc","tid":502924,"uid":3908,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:21:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"329ab09529d80c0dafc85405734d879822131ddf","tid":502924,"uid":78622,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:21:46.000Z","msg":"佢屌緊女唔得閒理妳姐"},{"pid":"5b0401ad00ac3c5a5628beff237a18ee9d94d540","tid":502924,"uid":163373,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:25:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢屌緊女唔得閒理妳姐</blockquote><br />\n可能係，呢幾個月失聯時間多左，然後話同朋友去左飲野"},{"pid":"e32dbd106b0419a6c6a44be658a2f8bd2bc8d1e2","tid":502924,"uid":163373,"like":1,"dislike":25,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:28:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>知道仲唔分手?<br />\n留係到做免費雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n佢唔認，我唔心息"},{"pid":"669347ff6499e6a87fe46fb344bef7bcbd6af6cb","tid":502924,"uid":160050,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:30:28.000Z","msg":"醒啦 分手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc587569a0cd36cea66306ad3a893c5d228fb911","tid":502924,"uid":163373,"l